Title : Alexander Hamilton (footballer, born 1865)
Text : {{Use dmy dates|date=September 2017}}
{{Use British English|date=September 2017}}
'''Alexander Hamilton''' (born July 1865)<ref name = "smith">{{harv|Smith|2013|p=113}}</ref> was a Scottish [[association football|footballer]], who played for [[Queen's Park F.C.|Queen's Park]] and represented [[Scotland national football team|Scotland]] four times.<ref>{{SFA Profile|id=113078|name=Alexander Hamilton}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.londonhearts.com/scotland/players/alexanderhamilton.html |title=Alexander Hamilton |work=www.londonhearts.com |publisher=London Hearts Supporters' Club |date= |accessdate=26 April 2014}}</ref>

Hamilton was the eldest of three brothers to play for Scotland, the others being [[Gladstone Hamilton|Gladstone]] and [[James Hamilton (Scottish footballer)|James]].<ref name = "smith"/>

